<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contacto — Metal-Ce S.R.L.</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navBar.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11"></script>
    <style>
        body { background: #f8f5f6; }

        .form-page-hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B1538 0%, #A91D47 50%, #6B0F2A 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 20px 80px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .form-page-hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; inset: 0;
            background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.04'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E") repeat;
        }
        .form-page-hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; position: relative; }
        .form-page-hero p  { font-size: 1.1rem; opacity: .85; position: relative; }

        .form-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 50px 50px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 50px rgba(139,21,56,0.1);
            max-width: 720px;
            margin: -50px auto 60px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .form-section-title {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #8B1538;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .form-section-title::after {
            content: '';
            flex: 1;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(139,21,56,0.2), transparent);
        }

        .form-group label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            font-size: .9rem;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .required-star { color: #8B1538; }

        .form-control {
            border: 2px solid #eee;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: .95rem;
            transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s;
        }
        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: #8B1538;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(139,21,56,0.1);
            outline: none;
        }

        .btn-submit {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B1538 0%, #A91D47 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
            letter-spacing: .5px;
        }
        .btn-submit:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(139,21,56,0.4);
        }

        .alert-custom-success {
            background: #f0fdf4;
            border: 2px solid #22c55e;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            color: #166534;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .alert-custom-error {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 2px solid #f87171;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            color: #991b1b;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .alert-custom-success i, .alert-custom-error i { font-size: 1.5rem; }

        .contact-side-info {
            max-width: 720px;
            margin: 0 auto 60px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .contact-side-info .row > div {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .info-pill {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(139,21,56,0.07);
            border-left: 4px solid #8B1538;
            height: 100%;
        }
        .info-pill i { color: #8B1538; font-size: 1.3rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .info-pill strong { display: block; color: #222; font-size: .88rem; }
        .info-pill span { color: #666; font-size: .84rem; }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .form-card { padding: 30px 20px; margin: -30px 12px 40px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbarUser') %>

    <div class="form-page-hero">
        <h1><i class="fas fa-envelope" style="margin-right:12px;"></i>Contactanos</h1>
        <p>Consultá precios, pedí cotización o solicitá asesoramiento técnico</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="form-card">

            <% if (enviado === true) { %>
            <div class="alert-custom-success">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                <div>
                    <strong>¡Mensaje enviado correctamente!</strong>
                    <span>Te responderemos a la brevedad. Revisá tu bandeja de entrada.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <% } %>
            <% if (enviado === false && error) { %>
            <div class="alert-custom-error">
                <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i>
                <div><strong>Error:</strong> <%= error %></div>
            </div>
            <% } %>

            <% if (enviado !== true) { %>
            <form action="/contacto" method="POST">

                <div class="form-section-title"><i class="fas fa-user"></i> Tus datos</div>

                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Nombre completo <span class="required-star">*</span></label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="nombre" placeholder="Juan García" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Empresa / Razón social</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="empresa" placeholder="Mi Empresa S.A. (opcional)">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Email <span class="required-star">*</span></label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" name="email" placeholder="tu@email.com" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Teléfono</label>
                            <input type="tel" class="form-control" name="telefono" placeholder="+54 9 351 ...">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-section-title" style="margin-top:10px;"><i class="fas fa-comment-dots"></i> Consulta</div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Tipo de consulta <span class="required-star">*</span></label>
                    <select class="form-control" name="tipo_consulta" required>
                        <option value="">— Seleccioná una opción —</option>
                        <option value="Cotización de productos">💰 Cotización de productos</option>
                        <option value="Información técnica">🔧 Información técnica</option>
                        <option value="Disponibilidad de stock">📦 Disponibilidad de stock</option>
                        <option value="Condiciones de pago">💳 Condiciones de pago</option>
                        <option value="Otro">📝 Otro</option>
                    </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Mensaje <span class="required-star">*</span></label>
                    <textarea class="form-control" name="mensaje" rows="5" placeholder="Describirme tu consulta con la mayor cantidad de detalle posible..." required></textarea>
                </div>

                <p style="font-size:.8rem;color:#999;margin-bottom:18px;">Los campos marcados con <span class="required-star">*</span> son obligatorios.</p>

                <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">
                    <i class="fas fa-paper-plane" style="margin-right:8px;"></i>Enviar consulta
                </button>
            </form>
            <% } else { %>
            <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:20px;">
                <a href="/" class="btn-submit" style="display:inline-block;text-decoration:none;width:auto;padding:14px 32px;">
                    <i class="fas fa-home" style="margin-right:8px;"></i>Volver al inicio
                </a>
            </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <!-- Info lateral debajo del form -->
        <div class="contact-side-info">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="info-pill">
                        <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                        <div><strong>Dirección</strong><span>Av. Colón 4160, Córdoba</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="info-pill">
                        <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                        <div><strong>Horarios</strong><span>Lun–Vie 8–18 · Sáb 8–13</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="info-pill">
                        <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i>
                        <div><strong>WhatsApp directo</strong><span><a href="https://wa.me/5493512345678" target="_blank" style="color:#8B1538;">+54 9 351 234-5678</a></span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.3/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
